**Hook Integration Pattern:**
- Destructure `{ toasts, show: showToast, hide: hideToast }` from useToast()
- Call showToast with options object containing style, title, and optional message
- Pass toasts and hideToast to ToastContainer at bottom of render
- All three styles (success, info, error) used throughout the app

